snippet.title: Playtime with Percy - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
GAMEJOLT PAGE: https://gamejolt.com/games/PwP/669217
DISCORD SERVER: https://discord.com/invite/7n37yVF5Sk

After the failure of the latest entertainment establishment; Percy's Playhouse. Your boss gives you a call, asking if you can watch over the now defunct play-place until it gets demolished at the end of the week. Fortunately, your PAL Percy isn't letting that happen, and he and his lackeys will make sure of it.

Thank you for supporting the development of Playtime with Percy! A team of 20+ people spent the last 1.5 years putting this project together. Please check it out when it releases AUGUST 4TH!
